(861, 861, 'ἀφθαρσία', '{\"def\":{\"short\":\"incorruptibility; genitive, unending existence; (figuratively) genuineness\",\"long\":[\"incorruption, perpetuity\",\"purity, sincerity, incorrupt\"]},\"deriv\":\"from G0862\",\"pronun\":{\"ipa\":\"ɑ.fθɑrˈsi.ɑ\",\"ipa_mod\":\"ɑ.fθɑrˈsi.ɑ\",\"sbl\":\"aphtharsia\",\"dic\":\"ah-fthahr-SEE-ah\",\"dic_mod\":\"ah-fthahr-SEE-ah\"},\"see\":[\"G0862\"]}', 'immortality, incorruption, sincerity'),
